                        <h2>About Me</h2>
                        
                        <h3>The Journey So Far</h3>
                        <p>
                            My journey into Android development began in 2024, driven by a curiosity to push the limits of what my devices could do. What started as simple experiments with modded ROMs has evolved into a passion for building stable, high-quality ported OEM ROMs.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            I believe strongly in the open-source spirit. By collaborating with friends and building upon the incredible work of the community, I strive to deliver reliable software experiences. I am constantly learning, debugging, and refining my skills to contribute back to the ecosystem that taught me so much.
                        </p>

                        <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
                            <a href="https://github.com/Dityay" target="_blank" class="m3-button filled" style="padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem;">Check my GitHub</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
